PROGRAMMING ASSETS ARE GENERALLY RECORDED WHEN THE PROGRAMMING BECOMES AVAILABLE TO US WITH A CORRESPONDING INCREASE IN PROGRAMMING LIABILITIES. ACCORDINGLY, WE ANALYZE OUR PROGRAMMING ASSETS NET OF THE RELATED LIABILITY.

