AND REQUIRE IT TO MEET CERTAIN ANNUAL FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE COVENANTS. SUBJECT TO FINAL THIRD-PARTY REVIEW AS PROVIDED IN ITS DEBT AGREEMENTS, EURO DISNEY BELIEVES THAT IT HAS COMPLIED WITH ITS FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE COVENANTS FOR FISCAL

