THE COMPANYS TOTAL ACCUMULATED PENSION BENEFIT OBLIGATIONS AT BOTH SEPTEMBER 27, 2008 AND SEPTEMBER 29, 2007 WAS $4.8 BILLION, OF WHICH

97.0% AND 96.2%, RESPECTIVELY, WERE VESTED.

